rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Maybe this place used to be covered
in trees and flowers like Gula...

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0101
rows.name:
This is a water tower, right?
What's one of those doing here?

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0201
rows.name: Tora seen tower like this in Gula!

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0202
rows.name:
Was Eden like Gula
long time ago?

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0301
rows.name:
I suppose the people of Eden
stored their water supply in towers,
just like we do ourselves.

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0302
rows.name:
Perhaps our societies were not as
different as they might seem.

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0401
rows.name:
If it was in Alst, I'd say this was
for storing water...

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0402
rows.name:
But who knows what the people
living here might've stored in it.
